{"id":599093,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【立此存照】此微博亲身演绎言论自由/","date":"2018-11-08T08:54:08Z","modified":"2018-11-08T09:02:11Z","title":"【立此存照】此微博亲身演绎言论自由","content":"<p>11月7日，中国接受联合国人权理事会第三轮国别人权审查。其间，中国外交部副部长乐玉成驳斥了“中国压制言论自由”的观点。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DrdT9MxWsAAgzw7.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599155\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DrdT9MxWsAAgzw7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DrdT9MxWsAAgzw7.jpg 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DrdT9MxWsAAgzw7-139x300.jpg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DrdT9MxWsAAgzw7-473x1024.jpg 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>11月8日，有网友发现，报道了此消息的国内媒体 @燃新闻 ，<a href=\"http://t.cn/EA7AWST\">相关视频</a>已被屏蔽，与此同时该微博下的所有<a href=\"https://weibo.com/6393904893/H1CssbvIE?type=comment\">网民评论</a>都被删除，亲身演绎是否“中国压制言论自由”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599151\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"412\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽.jpg 742w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽-300x247.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599152\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽2.jpg 783w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽2-300x155.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/屏蔽2-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Drdpa1qUUAA4bMi.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-599150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Drdpa1qUUAA4bMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"522\" height=\"507\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Drdpa1qUUAA4bMi.jpg 522w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Drdpa1qUUAA4bMi-300x291.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/Drdpa1qUUAA4bMi-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 522px) 100vw, 522px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/894ae2bdly1fx0q2pqks5j20qo0ewmyq.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-599158\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/894ae2bdly1fx0q2pqks5j20qo0ewmyq.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/894ae2bdly1fx0q2pqks5j20qo0ewmyq.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/894ae2bdly1fx0q2pqks5j20qo0ewmyq-300x167.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[36810,36811,36809,14912,8620,9212]}